{"title":"测桩，时代的宣言","authors":["纪钦"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":2,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"测桩，时代的宣言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纪钦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在天与地之间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我举起十八磅大锤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起力和热情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起一身的奋发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在荒凉和繁华的结合部上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在空白和充实的分界线上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在昨天和今天的交叉点上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"楔入一个伟大的宣言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，测桩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个生命的破折号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为沉疴所赘的躯体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做着勃勃的注释"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一管搏击的号角"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为藏龙卧虎的地域"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥起征战的旗幡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一支坚强的笔——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓胀着力量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饱含着信念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为《建设报》编发头条新闻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有读到它的人，都"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激动得燃起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的血液和爱情……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，测桩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"按着桩头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象总统按着《圣经》就职"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象苏丹按着《可兰经》宣誓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在天与地之间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在草莽和电子琴雄浑的交响中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在现实和理想奇妙的交汇中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我宣布，拢着自己的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从一个峡谷到另一个峡谷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从一个荒原到另一个荒原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里不再属于荒芜与兽迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里属于铜像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"属于纪念碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"属于博物馆……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}